{"tid":940699,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"維族男子誤遭德國遣返中國 證實被羈押中","createTime":"2018-12-14T06:51:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-14T07:42:51.000Z","uid":75969,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"8a11b162fd8185bf5e39783f90fbac9db50c0a07","tid":940699,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T06:51:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181214/large/1544760286_8aef.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181214%2Flarge%2F1544760286_8aef.jpg&h=085de554&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今年4月，誤遭德國當局遣返中國的維族難民，其下落終被確認。中國當局正以分裂國家或煽動分裂國家罪名，對他進行刑事訴訟。德國官方以及該維族難民的律師，對其能重返德國不抱太大希望。德國外交部確認，該名22歲維族男子4月初遭遣返中國後，就處於被羈押狀態，惟外交部並未透露其被羈押地點。<br />\n<br />\n德國外交部人權專員考夫勒(B&auml;rbel Kofler)表示，她於本月6日、7日參加於西藏拉薩舉行的德中人權對話時，向中方談及此議題。中國與會代表向她確認，該維族男子被羈押的消息。<br />\n<br />\n德國律師博格曼(Leo Borgmann)則透露，他的當事人因為德國官僚機構的一系列錯誤而遭遣返，目前被中國當局以分裂國家或煽動分裂國家罪名提出檢控。首場庭審已於10月13日進行。博格曼指出，雖然他不清楚中國當局究竟掌握哪些證據，但很可能與當事人曾在德國參加維族示威遊行有關。<br />\n<br />\n根據德國公共廣播聯盟的調查，今年3月29日，德國聯邦移民難民署向該名22歲維族男子寫了一封信：「請務必在4月3日上午9時30分參加此次政治避難申請聽證。」按照計劃，該維族男子應該在當天陳述其再次申請政治庇護的理由。但他未有參加該次聽證，並於4月3日清晨，被強制遣返中國。<br />\n<br />\n德國之聲  <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20181214/59028519\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181214%2F59028519&d=NgsX4dvaM60oeQzAHgI6lJUc5Mn1qk%2F8nAzLhrzJJK4%3D&h=2e402cdc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181214%2F59028519&h=9cf420e5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20181214/59028519</a><br />\n<br />\n送返入地獄鬼國 RIP<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"854ed019bcf178e98edcbae31d01795de7c8edbe","tid":940699,"uid":79563,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T06:52:06.000Z","msg":"德國死肥婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b9f0591fbfa4fb778c56a018acb2a01b3e2914d","tid":940699,"uid":93986,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T06:52:08.000Z","msg":"德國人落地獄啦"},{"pid":"f00cec39f09ea06313afbb93c7bde7a213a0f88e","tid":940699,"uid":125030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T06:53:05.000Z","msg":"咩叫誤遭遣返"},{"pid":"58418db35e4725acb60808c49a88df33d2b974d1","tid":940699,"uid":148749,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"f00cec39f09ea06313afbb93c7bde7a213a0f88e","tid":940699,"uid":125030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T06:53:05.000Z","msg":"咩叫誤遭遣返"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T06:55:14.000Z","msg":"send錯疏"},{"pid":"d2a4e089e1025776dc046fe2d82001b989e9ce67","tid":940699,"uid":152123,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T07:15:50.000Z","msg":"鬼叫你唔係敘利亞人咩"},{"pid":"b7c42118cf55fee18fa77e33f00f3bccd758483c","tid":940699,"uid":9726,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T07:26:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3ea059d1cc309c4b449aa1a472a5b959ec8a625d","tid":940699,"uid":56428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T07:29:19.000Z","msg":"南亞就唔趕  維族就趕 鬼婆"},{"pid":"28237c3e69ff568b3108f0c83af896caffccf309","tid":940699,"uid":171107,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T07:30:54.000Z","msg":"死鬼婆舔共舔到出晒面"},{"pid":"54bcbc8d442913e90eb960924d62b83df5a81faa","tid":940699,"uid":44454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T07:31:48.000Z","msg":"根本歷史上咁多年， 女人執正都冇好結果"},{"pid":"916c763364f325f11e70f2e66ac25447e4ca2fe3","tid":940699,"uid":73856,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3ea059d1cc309c4b449aa1a472a5b959ec8a625d","tid":940699,"uid":56428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T07:29:19.000Z","msg":"南亞就唔趕  維族就趕 鬼婆"},"citedBy":0